tial configuration done through VTYSH\n#\ncat >/tmp/config <<CONFIG\nhostname spine\n!\nlog file /tmp/logging\n\n!\nip forwarding\nvrf mgmt\n exit-vrf\n!\nfrr defaults datacenter\n!\ninterface lo\n no shutdown\n ip address 10.0.0.1/32\n!\ninterface eth1\n no shutdown\n description spine -> l1 [external]\n ip address 10.0.0.1/32\n ipv6 nd ra-interval 5\n no ipv6 nd suppress-ra\n!\ninterface eth2\n no shutdown\n description spine -> l2 [external]\n ip address 10.0.0.1/32\n ipv6 nd ra-interval 5\n no ipv6 nd suppress-ra\n!\ndo write\nCONFIG\nvtysh -f /tmp/config\n!\nexit 0\n"
}
